  "detailed_description": "Come and experience the fun of shooting and slam dunk!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090660/extras/20e8573acfc40f493431a9f9912309d2.avif?t=1662546043\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br>Points mall, you can buy characters and basketball court skins.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090660/extras/4bbf0fd7b6354cd92468952c93148a31.avif?t=1662546043\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br>Game mode: you can select practice mode, breakthrough mode and challenge mode. Let's start the challenge journey!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090660/extras/1418020ab3bf5c8715b7704b70d0f000.avif?t=1662546043\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br>Practice mode, unlimited shooting practice, find the feeling of shooting.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090660/extras/6f399bc6a3ea7e885df6d2168dcfe7ec.avif?t=1662546043\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br>Breakthrough mode: shoot from 5 positions, and all the shots are successful.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090660/extras/9c70a12d2275e929c7e173e93df7cd8b.avif?t=1662546043\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br>Challenge mode, choose an opponent to start the challenge!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2090660/extras/36e9731157b38cf3befcc5ef6837e826.avif?t=1662546043\" width=616 height=346 /></span>",
